label: The Charleston Earthquake, 1886
description: Photographs of the damage caused by the Charleston Earthquake of 1886. Photos are captioned with details, including the dollar amount of the damage.  Introductory text by Alex. M. Cochran.  Also includes advertisements for a variety of Charleston businesses, trades, merchants, and professionals.  Publisher unknown.  70 p.; 24 cm.
